Description: This is the accompanying R package for the paper
    "Goodness-of-fit tests for composite likelihood estimation under
    simple random and complex survey sampling". After fitting a binary
    factor model in lavaan, the user can call several functions to compute
    the goodness-of-fit test statistics based off of lower order marginals
    and compute the corresponding p-values.
